805
00:59:40,569 --> 00:59:41,940
Selamat hari Natal.

806
00:59:43,940 --> 00:59:45,609
Setiap momen berharga.

807
00:59:45,980 --> 00:59:47,280
Jangan bertengkar.

808
00:59:47,809 --> 00:59:50,050
Ini hari Natal.

809
00:59:56,389 --> 00:59:57,790
Ini juga kali pertamaku.

810
00:59:59,020 --> 01:00:00,329
Karena kamu.

811
01:00:22,510 --> 01:00:24,180
Astaga, laut.

812
01:00:25,849 --> 01:00:28,819
Halo, Lautan. Aku di sini!

813
01:00:33,059 --> 01:00:34,659
Selamat Natal!

814
01:01:07,629 --> 01:01:09,030
Pak Gu!

815
01:01:15,800 --> 01:01:17,339
Di sini indah!

816
01:01:24,379 --> 01:01:25,839
Kamu dengar ombaknya?

817
01:01:41,730 --> 01:01:44,899
Terima kasih sudah mengajakku kemari!

