828
01:03:23,559 --> 01:03:24,760
Kamu akan terserang flu.

829
01:03:24,760 --> 01:03:26,059
Ganti pakaianmu dahulu.

830
01:03:26,159 --> 01:03:27,669
Begitu kamu berganti pakaian,

831
01:03:28,500 --> 01:03:31,040
